title: Japan : number of internet users 2017 to 2023
yAxis: Number of internet users in millions
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Number of internet users in millions, containing a total of 7 data points.
Overall Number of internet users in millions has increased over the Year.
Number of internet users in millions is slightly increasing from 2017 to 2018, and finally roughly constant from 2018 to 2023.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2017 and 2018.
Maximum Number of internet users in millions, about 117.9 was reported at Year 2019,  2020, and 2021
The lowest Number of internet users in millions, of value 115.8 was reported at Year 2017
